  "description": "Armorer Villagers now take care of Iron Golems, helping them stay strong and ready to defend the village. [1.21.9 - 26.1.x]",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Armorer Heal Golem</h1>\n  <br/>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/armorer-heal-golem.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Wiki-Armorer%20Heal%20Golem-gold?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt=\"Wiki Link\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Release-1.1.x-limegreen\" alt=\"Release\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.21.9%2026.1.x-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,&logoWidth=50\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-blueviolet\" alt=\"License CC BY 4.0\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tq83Zuhduv\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1358706268012810350?color=5865F2&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/CPKlbUiJ?logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<h3>🧪 Main description</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  This module allows armorer villagers to naturally care for Iron Golems, helping them recover and stay strong while defending the village.<br/> \n  It adds a subtle and immersive touch to gameplay, making villages feel more alive and interconnected.\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚡ Use and benefits</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Keeps your Iron Golems in good condition without requiring player intervention.<br/>\n  Enhances village survival and immersion by making armorer villagers feel more helpful and alive.\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Technical informations</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Armorer Villagers are able to heal nearby Iron Golems, restoring 4 health points (2 hearts) each time.<br/>\n  This healing effect is automatically applied every 3 seconds, helping golems stay strong while protecting the village.\n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>🎬 Video</h2>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/gr_m_sjcFbA\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📖 Wiki</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  <a href=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/armorer-heal-golem.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n    https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/armorer-heal-golem.html\n  </a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📥 Installation</h2>\n<h3>📁 Datapack</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.zip</code> file into your world's <code>datapacks</code> folder.<br/>\n  Reload the world or use <code>/reload</code>.<br/>\n  Enjoy your enchanted adventure!\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Mod</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.jar</code> file into the <code>mods</code> folder of your instance.<br/>\n  <code>Restart</code> your game.<br/>\n  Have fun!\n</blockquote>",
